# Prompt Library

A collection of reusable prompts organized by category. These prompts are **not automatically applied** - they only load when explicitly referenced.

## How to Use

Reference prompts using the `@` syntax in your Cursor chat:

```
@prompt-library/category prompt-name Your specific request here
```

